OL,3,CChildren 'sleeping in baths' because
OL,4,Cparents can't afford beds
OL,6,FThe Beds for Babies initiative aims to
OL,7,Fensure children who need a bed, Moses
OL,8,Fbasket, cot or toddler bed get one.
OL,10,FMs Ross said: "We know that (the
OL,11,Fscheme) is not just about the
OL,12,Fprovision of that tangible bed, it's
OL,13,Fabout the housing these people are in,
OL,14,Fit's about the other support that's
OL,15,Fneeded.
OL,17,F"Our hope is that by the professionals
OL,18,Fbeing able to provide that bed via us,
OL,19,Fthat will help to broker that trusted
OL,20,Frelationship."
