OL,3,CChildren 'sleeping in baths' because
OL,4,Cparents can't afford beds
OL,6,FMr Coppard said the issue was part of
OL,7,Fa "wider problem" in the economy.
OL,9,FHe said: "We need to step in to
OL,10,Fsupport wherever we can.
OL,12,F"Thats why we put in place the beds
OL,13,Ffor babies scheme, that's why we put
OL,14,Fhelp in place for any family that
OL,15,Fneeds it."
