OL,3,CChildren 'sleeping in baths' because
OL,4,Cparents can't afford beds
OL,6,FProf Sally Pearse, from Sheffield
OL,7,FHallam University, said: "Research
OL,8,Fshows that good quality, safe sleep is
OL,9,Fvital for healthy child development so
OL,10,Fthis initiative is also supporting
OL,11,Fchildren's long-term health and giving
OL,12,Fthem a better start in life.J"Parents
OL,13,Fin many of our communities are
OL,14,Fstruggling with multiple challenges.
